VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?i)\b(SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE|CSRF_COOKIE_SECURE)\s*=\s*False\b
WHEN EXPR MISSING:SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE\s*=\s*True|CSRF_COOKIE_SECURE\s*=\s*True|production|test|example
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects potential security vulnerabilities related to insecure session cookies or CSRF token configurations in Django and similar Python web frameworks.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Insecure Session Cookies or CSRF Tokens Configuration.
